exercise.instructions:
1. After the HYUN_FIRST_ResetAppCmd() function protoype definition add the HYUN_FIRST_SetParamCmd() definition:
    bool HYUN_FIRST_SetParamCmd(void *ObjDataPtr, const CFE_MSG_Message_t *MsgPtr);
    Note this isn't required to compile the code, but is good practice if the function needs to be accessed by a unit test.

1. After the last CMDMGR_RegisterFunc() add
    CMDMGR_RegisterFunc(CMDMGR_OBJ, HYUN_FIRST_SET_PARAM_CC, NULL, HYUN_FIRST_SetParamCmd, sizeof(HYUN_FIRST_SetParam_CmdPayload_t));

Note HYUN_FIRST_SET_PARAM_CMD_CC is generated by the EDS toolchain
